\n\nIf this policy is enabled, the option to import search engine settings is automatically selected.\n\nIf this policy is disabled, search engine settings are not imported at first run, and users cannot import them manually.","false_positives":"","false_negatives":"","documentable":"false","security_override_guidance":"","potential_impacts":"","third_party_tools":"","ia_controls":"","responsibility":"","mitigations":"","mitigation_control":"","ccis":["CCI-000381"],"reference_identifier":"5280","uuid":"7b2f7929-ade7-48fc-a1fd-f8b6bbd48c68","stig_uuid":"dfe3f216-ed6b-4fdf-8f52-fddf7eadd2aa","status":"open","overrides":{},"comments":"","finding_details":"Evaluate-STIG 1.2604.2 (Scan-MicrosoftEdge_Checks) found this to be OPEN on 07/22/2026\r\nResultHash: BC9A18C42F993E182844021E09F9CC890D8CF792\r\n~~~~~\r\n'Computer Configuration/Administrative Templates/Microsoft Edge/Allow importing of search engine settings' is NOT Disabled\r\n\r\nRegistry Path:\tHKLM:\\SOFTWARE\\Policies\\Microsoft\\Edge\r\nValue Name:\tImportSearchEngine (Not found)"},{"group_id_src":"V-235740","group_tree":[{"id":"V-235740","title":"SRG-APP-000141","description":"<GroupDescription></GroupDescription>"}],"group_id":"V-235740","severity":"medium","group_title":"Importing of shortcuts must be disabled.","rule_id_src":"SV-235740r960963_rule","rule_id":"SV-235740r960963","rule_version":"EDGE-00-000023","rule_title":"Importing of shortcuts must be disabled.","fix_text":"Set the policy value for \"Computer Configuration/Administrative Templates/Microsoft Edge/Allow importing of shortcuts\" to \"disabled\".","weight":"10.0","check_content":"The policy value for \"Computer Configuration/Administrative Templates/Microsoft Edge/Allow importing of shortcuts\" must be set to \"disabled\".\n\nUse the Windows Registry Editor to navigate to the following key:\nHKLM\\SOFTWARE\\Policies\\Microsoft\\Edge\n\nIf the value for \"ImportShortcuts\" is not set to \"REG_DWORD = 0\", this is a finding.","check_content_ref